    "Yet industry has a strong hold on academia and advocacy because it constitutes a key funding source and potential career trajectory.",
    "In China, the government is the dominant stakeholder shaping AI development; academia plays a passive and ambivalent role in the AI stakeholder landscape.",
    "Various professors and other academics are prominently represented in the AI industry.",
    "There is consensus on the importance of academic research on AI to cover relevant but neglected topics by the Chinese AI sector, often critiqued for emphasising the technologies economic over societal benefits.",
    "At the same time, many interviewed experts lament that academia lags behind industry in AI research."
